142
00:05:53,680 --> 00:05:55,560
I do. I'm here for the money.

143
00:05:55,560 --> 00:05:56,600
I'm here to learn.

144
00:05:56,600 --> 00:05:57,720
Did you see the scene of me?

145
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:59,080
He is your friend, right?

146
00:05:59,800 --> 00:06:00,440
I'll ask him.

147
00:06:00,440 --> 00:06:01,000
Well...

148
00:06:01,400 --> 00:06:02,000
I-I...

149
00:06:02,800 --> 00:06:04,080
H-He's really going, huh?

150
00:06:04,720 --> 00:06:05,680
Let them talk.

151
00:06:06,320 --> 00:06:07,680
Director! Hello, sir.

152
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:09,120
I'm a friend of your buddy,

153
00:06:09,120 --> 00:06:10,560
Xu Xiangdong.

154
00:06:10,560 --> 00:06:11,320
Xu Xiangdong?

155
00:06:11,800 --> 00:06:13,680
Who's that? Never heard of him.

156
00:06:14,880 --> 00:06:15,600
Do you know him?

157
00:06:18,800 --> 00:06:19,960
