225
00:08:06,880 --> 00:08:07,840
Are you kidding?

226
00:08:09,080 --> 00:08:10,600
What a terrible performance!

227
00:08:10,600 --> 00:08:12,000
One idiot even laughed.

228
00:08:13,120 --> 00:08:13,960
What a joke!

229
00:08:13,960 --> 00:08:14,960
Back in my younger days,

230
00:08:14,960 --> 00:08:16,400
I would knock their socks off.

231
00:08:17,320 --> 00:08:18,320
Really interesting.

232
00:08:19,720 --> 00:08:20,560
You three.

233
00:08:21,408 --> 00:08:22,000
Are you...

234
00:08:22,000 --> 00:08:22,680
We three, yeah,

235
00:08:22,680 --> 00:08:24,160
