236
00:08:24,160 --> 00:08:25,240
F-F-Fans.

237
00:08:25,720 --> 00:08:26,320
Fans?

238
00:08:26,440 --> 00:08:27,880
You three are zombies!

239
00:08:28,080 --> 00:08:28,800
Assistant Director!

240
00:08:29,080 --> 00:08:30,680
Get them out!

241
00:08:31,080 --> 00:08:31,880
Quickly!

242
00:08:31,880 --> 00:08:33,120
- Oh, no.
- Get them out!

243
00:08:33,120 --> 00:08:33,720
Assistant Director!

244
00:08:33,720 --> 00:08:35,680
Get the three guys out!

245
00:08:35,680 --> 00:08:36,520
Throw them out.

246
00:08:37,960 --> 00:08:39,080
