249
00:08:44,040 --> 00:08:45,480
250 yuan each.

250
00:08:46,920 --> 00:08:48,960
Yeah, we're the real fools now.
[*The number 250 means fools in Chinese]

251
00:08:51,720 --> 00:08:52,360
Look,

252
00:08:52,960 --> 00:08:55,840
I took you there mainly for learning

253
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:57,080
and to earn a bit as well.

254
00:08:57,080 --> 00:08:58,360
