about his script?

262
00:09:14,920 --> 00:09:18,200
A mix of a comic, a skit,

263
00:09:18,200 --> 00:09:19,960
dancing and singing.

264
00:09:20,920 --> 00:09:21,640
Total nonsense!

265
00:09:21,960 --> 00:09:23,080
Even Xiao Rang is better.

266
00:09:24,640 --> 00:09:26,480
You're not complimenting me, right?

267
00:09:26,640 --> 00:09:28,360
Young man, you don't understand.

268
00:09:28,520 --> 00:09:30,480
If you want to produce good films,

269
00:09:30,480 --> 00:09:33,160
you have to humble yourself and learn.

270
00:09:34,080 --> 00:09:34,600
Oh, right.

271
00:09:34,600 --> 00:09:35,920
I've returned your DV camera.

272
00:09:36,080 --> 00:09:37,520
The tape inside is at my place.

273
00:09:37,520 --> 00:09:38,360
I'll give it back.

274
00:09:38,360 --> 00:09:40,160
Just connect that device to your phone,

275
00:09:40,160 --> 00:09:41,040
and you can see it.

276
00:09:41,200 --> 00:09:42,080
That's professional.

277
00:09:42,080 --> 00:09:43,280
Getting more professional.

278
00:09:43,280 --> 00:09:45,040
Now you know bringing that to me.

279
00:09:45,280 --> 00:09:47,280
I have always been professional.

280
00:09:48,200 --> 00:09:48,760
Mr. Dong,

281
00:09:49,520 --> 00:09:52,040
is that director

282
00:09:52,040 --> 00:09:52,960
really your buddy?

283
00:09:52,960 --> 00:09:54,400
He said he didn't know you.

284
00:09:56,360 --> 00:09:57,080
Of course we are.

285
00:09:57,080 --> 00:09:59,360
That director is just a small fry

286
00:09:59,360 --> 00:10:01,960
