Sure, we trust you.

289
00:10:07,400 --> 00:10:08,080
Especially with

290
00:10:08,080 --> 00:10:09,520
how he's paying us 250 a day.

291
00:10:09,520 --> 00:10:10,360
Very trustworthy!

292
00:10:12,360 --> 00:10:13,200
Mr. Dong,

293
00:10:13,600 --> 00:10:14,520
how about you

294
00:10:14,520 --> 00:10:15,520
wash your face carefully?

295
00:10:15,520 --> 00:10:16,520
I really want to learn

296
00:10:16,520 --> 00:10:18,640
how you can use your sincere face

297
00:10:18,640 --> 00:10:19,760
to talk big.

298
00:10:19,760 --> 00:10:20,640
Really.

299
00:10:20,720 --> 00:10:21,400
To talk big?

300
00:10:22,520 --> 00:10:23,160
Okay.

301
00:10:25,480 --> 00:10:26,760
Come on!

302
00:10:27,200 --> 00:10:28,040
- Come on!
- Pour it on me.

303
00:10:28,480 --> 00:10:29,360
- Go ahead!
- So cold!

304
00:10:31,200 --> 00:10:31,920
Hey!

305
00:10:34,360 --> 00:10:34,912
Stop it!

306
00:10:56,920 --> 00:10:57,760
Why not paint?

307
00:10:58,360 --> 00:10:59,160
Not in the mood.

308
00:10:59,600 --> 00:11:01,480
Did I bring you here to see the scenery?

309
00:11:02,760 --> 00:11:04,400
But now,
I just want to enjoy the scenery.

310
00:11:05,080 --> 00:11:05,720
Alright.

311
00:11:06,160 --> 00:11:07,760
Artistic mood is very important.

312
00:11:08,280 --> 00:11:09,520
You can skip today.

313
00:11:09,760 --> 00:11:11,840
But remember to make it up next week.

314
00:11:30,360 --> 00:11:31,960
You don't have the mood to paint today?

315
00:11:35,200 --> 00:11:37,080
Look, in our class, we are

316
00:11:37,080 --> 00:11:38,760
among the most brilliant ones.

317
00:11:39,280 --> 00:11:40,640
Why is it that every time we talk,

318
00:11:41,600 --> 00:11:42,640
we ended up arguing?

319
00:11:43,400 --> 00:11:45,040
I don't think you have anything

320
00:11:45,040 --> 00:11:45,960
to do with "brilliant".

321
00:11:47,360 --> 00:11:48,480
Oh, come on.

322
00:11:48,920 --> 00:11:49,640
Your arrogance

323
00:11:49,640 --> 00:11:51,400
brings you a vibe of a master.

324
00:11:52,520 --> 00:11:53,080
Okay.

325
00:11:53,080 --> 00:11:54,720
Let's settle this

326
00:11:54,920 --> 00:11:57,280
with a fair competition.

327
00:11:57,480 --> 00:11:58,112
Dare to?

328
00:11:58,112 --> 00:11:59,480
There is nothing to compete.

329
00:11:59,760 --> 00:12:00,760
You win.

330
00:12:00,760 --> 00:12:01,480
That won't do.

331
00:12:01,480 --> 00:12:03,960
My goal is to defeat you

332
00:12:03,960 --> 00:12:05,200
in front of the whole school.

333
00:12:05,360 --> 00:12:06,640
For a sense of achievement.

334
00:12:06,840 --> 00:12:07,960
Defeat me publicly?

335
00:12:08,480 --> 00:12:09,640
Right, dare or not?

336
00:12:11,200 --> 00:12:12,080
Not interested.

337
00:12:13,160 --> 00:12:14,040
Don't be a coward.

338
00:12:14,400 --> 00:12:15,040
How about this?

339
00:12:15,640 --> 00:12:17,200
I'll give you a chance

340
00:12:17,200 --> 00:12:18,840
to defeat me

341
00:12:18,840 --> 00:12:20,640
in front of the whole school, okay?

342
00:12:21,160 --> 00:12:22,040
Ridiculous.

343
00:12:22,480 --> 00:12:23,640
I'm even less interested.

344
00:12:24,160 --> 00:12:24,920
You wait.

345
00:12:25,040 --> 00:12:25,960
I will make you

346
00:12:25,960 --> 00:12:27,640
compete with me willingly.

347
00:12:34,360 --> 00:12:35,720
I heard what Huang Shan said.

348
00:12:36,160 --> 00:12:37,520
I think you should accept it.

349
00:12:38,360 --> 00:12:40,080
His paintings are only sold because of

350
00:12:40,080 --> 00:12:41,040
his father's promotion.

351
00:12:41,480 --> 00:12:42,640
I don't want to rival him.

352
00:12:43,040 --> 00:12:45,280
All the more reason for you to compete.

353
00:12:45,520 --> 00:12:46,920
Let everyone know

354
00:12:47,640 --> 00:12:48,920
the path he's taken is wrong.

355
00:13:04,920 --> 00:13:07,200
Director Wang sent me two movie tickets

356
00:13:07,480 --> 00:13:08,520
for tomorrow night.

357
00:13:08,520 --> 00:13:09,520
Who will go with me?

358
00:13:10,080 --> 00:13:11,080
I'm not going with you.

359
00:13:11,480 --> 00:13:13,360
Two men watching a movie together?
So weird.

360
00:13:13,720 --> 00:13:14,520
Fine.

361
00:13:14,920 --> 00:13:15,640
What about you?

362
00:13:18,484 --> 00:13:18,760
(Free Tickets
from Binhai University Cinema)

363
00:13:18,760 --> 00:13:20,400
(Free tickets)
Aren't these from our school?

364
00:13:24,360 --> 00:13:26,760
Director Wang has a partnership
with our school.

365
00:13:26,944 --> 00:13:27,480
Moreover,

366
00:13:27,480 --> 00:13:28,920
today we did on-site practice.

367
00:13:28,920 --> 00:13:30,360
Tomorrow we'll have film analysis.

368
00:13:30,640 --> 00:13:31,520
Take a look quickly.

369
00:13:31,520 --> 00:13:32,640
And then you can start

370
00:13:32,640 --> 00:13:33,920
our movie project.

371
00:13:34,080 --> 00:13:35,200
Hurry up, okay?

372
00:13:35,200 --> 00:13:36,600
I know.

373
00:13:36,600 --> 00:13:37,920
Tomorrow we'll see the movie.

374
00:13:37,920 --> 00:13:39,360
After that, we'll make a movie.

375
00:13:42,760 --> 00:13:43,760
We had a main course today.

376
00:13:43,760 --> 00:13:44,960
We forgot to attend it.

377
00:13:45,360 --> 00:13:47,480
Mrs. Jiang asked us
to go to her office tomorrow.

378
00:13:49,360 --> 00:13:50,840
Oh, no. Totally forgot it.

379
00:13:51,200 --> 00:13:52,080
So what do we do?

380
00:13:52,200 --> 00:13:53,360
How would I know what to do?

381
00:13:53,920 --> 00:13:55,080
Order more oysters.

382
00:13:55,760 --> 00:13:56,360
No way.

383
00:13:56,360 --> 00:13:57,520
You've ordered so much.

384
00:13:58,200 --> 00:13:59,640
We didn't make any money today.

385
00:13:59,640 --> 00:14:01,520
And there is highway costs, water bills,

386
00:14:01,520 --> 00:14:03,040
lost wages, and food expenses.

387
00:14:03,040 --> 00:14:03,960
Spent a bunch already.

388
00:14:03,960 --> 00:14:05,920
Let's walk back home tonight.

389
00:14:08,640 --> 00:14:10,200
Alright, we'll definitely go.

390
00:14:15,400 --> 00:14:16,520
Mr. Lei called me.

391
00:14:16,520 --> 00:14:17,760
He said that he's reopened

392
00:14:17,960 --> 00:14:19,040
and asked us to help him.

393
00:14:19,360 --> 00:14:21,400
This time he offers
a slightly higher pay.

394
00:14:21,760 --> 00:14:23,080
Want to go?

395
00:14:23,200 --> 00:14:23,840
Yeah!

396
00:14:24,360 --> 00:14:26,040
With so many pretty girls there,

397
00:14:26,040 --> 00:14:27,640
I might sooner get a girlfriend.

398
00:14:28,280 --> 00:14:29,360
We'll see about that.

399
00:14:29,480 --> 00:14:30,600
If the movie fund

400
00:14:30,600 --> 00:14:31,520
turns out to be enough,

401
00:14:31,520 --> 00:14:33,200
I need to focus on our script.

402
00:14:33,600 --> 00:14:34,600
Suit it yourself then.

403
00:14:35,040 --> 00:14:35,920
We will go tomorrow.

404
00:14:35,920 --> 00:14:36,640
Okay, let's go.

405
00:14:38,480 --> 00:14:40,200
But I have an important thing
next morning.

406
00:14:40,520 --> 00:14:41,360
What is it?

407
00:14:43,400 --> 00:14:45,480
Showing my true strength

408
00:14:45,720 --> 00:14:48,160
and fighting for the honor of us three!

409
00:14:53,299 --> 00:14:53,952
(You Rong Boxing)

410
00:15:03,080 --> 00:15:03,920
Stop right there.

411
00:15:06,760 --> 00:15:08,640
I'm not done yet. Rematch!

412
00:16:17,760 --> 00:16:18,920
Great. Don't drop the ball.

413
00:16:18,920 --> 00:16:20,480
Alright, shoot!

414
00:16:20,920 --> 00:16:21,480
Shoot!

415
00:16:22,640 --> 00:16:23,280
Shoot!

416
00:16:23,480 --> 00:16:24,080
Good.

417
00:16:24,080 --> 00:16:24,920
Li Yanhao.

418
00:16:25,840 --> 00:16:26,400
Terrible shot.

419
00:16:26,760 --> 00:16:27,520
Li Yanhao.

420
00:16:29,640 --> 00:16:30,200
Yu Lan?

421
00:16:30,760 --> 00:16:31,600
Why are you here?

422
00:16:32,280 --> 00:16:33,760
I saw you filming so intently,

423
00:16:33,760 --> 00:16:34,720
so I came here.

424
00:16:36,760 --> 00:16:38,480
When working, I must always focus.

425
00:16:40,040 --> 00:16:41,160
Then I'm relieved.

426
00:16:41,400 --> 00:16:43,480
I was worried that after the meeting,

427
00:16:43,480 --> 00:16:44,480
you'd be down and out.

428
00:16:45,360 --> 00:16:46,200
No way.

429
00:16:46,760 --> 00:16:47,720
I'm a strong man.

430
00:16:47,720 --> 00:16:49,480
How could I be defeated
by just a few words?

431
00:16:51,280 --> 00:16:53,040
What have you shot? Let me have a look.

432
00:16:55,360 --> 00:16:56,920
Nothing, just random shots.

433
00:16:57,640 --> 00:16:59,640
Okay then, keep going.

434
00:16:59,760 --> 00:17:00,520
I'm leaving.

435
00:17:01,840 --> 00:17:02,480
Wait a minute.

436
00:17:20,360 --> 00:17:21,000
Let go.

437
00:17:22,752 --> 00:17:23,280
Let go!

438
00:17:23,280 --> 00:17:24,000
I won't let go.

439
00:17:24,360 --> 00:17:24,880
Let go!

440
00:17:24,880 --> 00:17:25,600
No way.

441
00:17:26,000 --> 00:17:27,280
Tell me, did I win or not?

442
00:17:40,120 --> 00:17:41,000
You won nothing!

443
00:17:44,600 --> 00:17:45,240
How's it going?

444
00:17:46,760 --> 00:17:48,120
Quite beyond my expectations.

445
00:17:48,480 --> 00:17:50,360
Although it's not quite a movie yet,

446
00:17:50,880 --> 00:17:52,240
I can see your imagination

447
00:17:52,240 --> 00:17:53,640
and the things you want to express.

448
00:17:54,360 --> 00:17:56,480
There must be imaginations.

449
00:17:57,520 --> 00:17:59,880
My script is still in progress.

450
00:18:00,240 --> 00:18:01,120
Creation, you know,

451
00:18:01,360 --> 00:18:03,000
requires boundless imagination

452
00:18:03,000 --> 00:18:05,000
and unlimited design.

453
00:18:06,760 --> 00:18:08,640
What kind of story do you plan to write?

454
00:18:11,240 --> 00:18:13,480
I'm thinking of
combining horror, musical,

455
00:18:13,480 --> 00:18:15,000
martial arts and fantasy into one.

456
00:18:15,600 --> 00:18:16,640
Among all the contestants,

457
00:18:16,640 --> 00:18:18,120
maybe only I dare to do that.

458
00:18:18,880 --> 00:18:20,520
Sounds a bit "juvenile".

459
00:18:22,160 --> 00:18:23,880
Right?

460
00:18:24,240 --> 00:18:25,120
I agree.

461
00:18:26,280 --> 00:18:27,880
Actually, a few days ago,

462
00:18:27,880 --> 00:18:29,880
when I went to learn at a film crew,

463
00:18:29,880 --> 00:18:31,000
the director told it to me.

464
00:18:31,000 --> 00:18:32,360
I didn't think it's good, either.

465
00:18:33,120 --> 00:18:35,360
You went to learn with a film crew?

466
00:18:38,880 --> 00:18:39,480
Oh, right.

467
00:18:39,480 --> 00:18:41,000
During that day,

468
00:18:41,760 --> 00:18:43,360
I noted down what I thought was useful

469
00:18:45,120 --> 00:18:46,360
all in this notebook.

470
00:18:46,739 --> 00:18:51,904
(Film)

471
00:18:57,600 --> 00:18:58,720
Your notebook

472
00:19:00,400 --> 00:19:01,280
is quite unique.

473
00:19:04,840 --> 00:19:05,400
Isn't it?

474
00:19:09,400 --> 00:19:10,080
Hello?

475
00:19:11,280 --> 00:19:12,080
Kang?

476
00:19:12,400 --> 00:19:13,720
Alright, I'll come right away.

477
00:19:16,600 --> 00:19:17,240
Uh...

478
00:19:21,160 --> 00:19:22,160
That's okay. Bye.

479
00:19:27,600 --> 00:19:28,840
Let's watch a movie together.

480
00:19:35,507 --> 00:19:40,960
(You Rong Boxing)

481
00:19:41,360 --> 00:19:43,120
Match's over. You still sneak attack me!

482
00:19:43,120 --> 00:19:44,120
Dishonorable!

483
00:19:44,600 --> 00:19:45,840
I must teach you a lesson.

484
00:19:46,080 --> 00:19:47,080
You didn't let go first.

485
00:19:48,080 --> 00:19:49,080
But honestly,

486
00:19:49,400 --> 00:19:52,480
I've never been so close
to a boy before.

487
00:19:52,600 --> 00:19:54,480
Isn't that normal in boxing?

488
00:19:54,720 --> 00:19:56,280
Besides, Li Yanhao and I

489
00:19:56,280 --> 00:19:57,600
used to wrestle in the mud

490
00:19:57,600 --> 00:19:58,600
shirtless every day.

491
00:19:58,760 --> 00:20:00,720
But you are both boys!

492
00:20:02,840 --> 00:20:04,000
You see yourself as a girl?

493
00:20:04,160 --> 00:20:04,760
You...

494
00:20:06,280 --> 00:20:07,640
You want another beating?

495
00:20:08,520 --> 00:20:09,160
Calm down, girl.

496
00:20:09,280 --> 00:20:10,720
You are a beauty rivals everything.

497
00:20:10,720 --> 00:20:11,720
Sorry.

498
00:20:12,960 --> 00:20:14,280
Can't make it up anymore.

499
00:20:17,720 --> 00:20:18,760
But honestly,

500
00:20:19,000 --> 00:20:21,960
you do have some manliness.

501
00:20:22,360 --> 00:20:24,600
Right? I knew it.

502
00:20:24,600 --> 00:20:26,480
You have sheen eyes.

503
00:20:26,840 --> 00:20:27,600
Just for that word,

504
00:20:27,600 --> 00:20:29,080
today's beating was worth it.

505
00:20:33,520 --> 00:20:34,160
I'm leaving.

506
00:20:39,280 --> 00:20:40,240
You have a girlfriend?

507
00:20:41,720 --> 00:20:42,280
No.

508
00:20:45,280 --> 00:20:46,240
Well, now you do.

509
00:20:48,600 --> 00:20:49,400
What?

510
00:20:50,600 --> 00:20:52,640
Just for being my human punching bag

511
00:20:52,640 --> 00:20:53,960
and your perseverance,

512
00:20:53,960 --> 00:20:54,840
I like you.

513
00:20:54,960 --> 00:20:56,960
From today, you accompany me
in fitness boxing.

514
00:21:01,280 --> 00:21:02,960
Or we could start dating today.

515
00:21:04,760 --> 00:21:06,080
Alright, no more nonsense.

516
00:21:06,080 --> 00:21:07,080
I'm off to take a shower.

517
00:21:07,080 --> 00:21:08,000
Keep my stuff safe.

518
00:21:26,760 --> 00:21:27,280
Your pancake.

519
00:21:42,960 --> 00:21:44,080
What are you thinking?

520
00:21:45,720 --> 00:21:46,520
Listen to me.

521
00:21:47,080 --> 00:21:47,760
Okay.

522
00:21:49,400 --> 00:21:50,840
I think I've got a girlfriend.

523
00:21:52,080 --> 00:21:52,720
What?

524
00:21:53,600 --> 00:21:55,080
I think I've got a girlfriend.

525
00:21:55,760 --> 00:21:57,280
Who is it? Who's so unlucky?

526
00:21:59,240 --> 00:21:59,960
The boxing queen,

527
00:22:00,400 --> 00:22:01,080
Gu Ran.

528
00:22:04,640 --> 00:22:06,600
Wow, seriously?

529
00:22:06,600 --> 00:22:07,400
That's awesome.

530
00:22:07,400 --> 00:22:08,280
Your face...

531
00:22:10,600 --> 00:22:11,240
Bro,

532
00:22:11,640 --> 00:22:12,640
didn't you

533
00:22:12,640 --> 00:22:13,840
sacrifice yourself for me?

534
00:22:13,840 --> 00:22:15,160
Bug off.

535
00:22:16,640 --> 00:22:18,080
She even asked me to date tonight.

536
00:22:18,280 --> 00:22:19,080
Nice!

537
00:22:20,280 --> 00:22:22,080
The closer you are with Gu Ran,

538
00:22:22,080 --> 00:22:23,000
means

539
00:22:23,000 --> 00:22:24,720
I'll see Yu Lan more often, right?

540
00:22:26,720 --> 00:22:28,080
But I have a feeling

541
00:22:28,080 --> 00:22:30,400
that she just wants someone to box with.

542
00:22:32,480 --> 00:22:34,160
Do you think my peaceful days are over?

543
00:22:34,520 --> 00:22:35,960
No. It's a good thing.

544
00:22:36,840 --> 00:22:38,280
You with Gu Ran, and I with Yu Lan.

545
00:22:38,520 --> 00:22:39,480
A happy family.

546
00:22:39,480 --> 00:22:40,240
Isn't that perfect?

547
00:22:40,960 --> 00:22:42,400
Are you listening to me or not?

548
00:22:43,520 --> 00:22:44,280
What did you say?

549
00:22:47,400 --> 00:22:48,640
Did you forget your vow

550
00:22:48,640 --> 00:22:49,760
when you entered college?

551
00:22:50,080 --> 00:22:51,880
To date 100 girls!

552
00:22:52,240 --> 00:22:53,720
This is a good start.

553
00:22:53,720 --> 00:22:55,600
But the first one
shouldn't be the end of me.

554
00:22:56,160 --> 00:22:56,960
Be content.

555
00:22:56,960 --> 00:22:58,280
At least you got one.

556
00:23:06,280 --> 00:23:07,600
Oh, no more eating.

557
00:23:07,840 --> 00:23:08,760
Mrs. Jiang wants us.

558
00:23:09,080 --> 00:23:09,640
Let's go.

559
00:23:14,080 --> 00:23:15,240
You, hand the test materials

560
00:23:15,240 --> 00:23:16,160
to the whole class.

561
00:23:16,160 --> 00:23:17,960
All the test questions are in here.

562
00:23:18,160 --> 00:23:19,400
Alright, you can go back.

563
00:23:19,600 --> 00:23:20,160
Okay.

564
00:23:25,960 --> 00:23:26,840
Hurry up.

565
00:23:27,795 --> 00:23:28,736
(Department of Library Management)

566
00:23:29,080 --> 00:23:29,840
Are you alright?

567
00:23:30,280 --> 00:23:32,280
Ran into my nemesis.

568
00:23:32,600 --> 00:23:33,640
Mrs. Jiang gives you this.

569
00:23:34,400 --> 00:23:36,880
I've always following her words.

570
00:23:39,080 --> 00:23:40,640
You've studied too much to be an idiot!

571
00:23:40,960 --> 00:23:41,880
No,

572
00:23:41,880 --> 00:23:43,280
he's sleeping too much!

573
00:23:57,400 --> 00:23:57,960
Mrs. Jiang.

574
00:23:57,960 --> 00:23:58,640
Tell me,

575
00:23:58,760 --> 00:24:00,160
why did you skip class yesterday?

576
00:24:00,160 --> 00:24:03,240
We were doing social practice yesterday.

577
00:24:03,520 --> 00:24:04,960
What social practice?

578
00:24:05,280 --> 00:24:07,120
More important than the major courses?

579
00:24:07,280 --> 00:24:09,120
Final exams are less than a month away.

